# <type>: <short summary>

# type: feat | fix | refactor | chore | docs | perf
# 
# feat     - new feature
# fix      - bug fix
# refactor - code restructure (no behavior change)
# chore    - build/tooling (PM2, gitignore, etc.)
# docs     - documentation
# perf     - performance improvement
# 
# Example:
#   feat: add worker efficiency dashboard
#   fix: resolve login 500 when session expires
